Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢调戏老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么呀你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了啦 夕子学姐
